These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, architect
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, adventure
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, house
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, golf
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, snowmobile
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the mechanic##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | water     | juice |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | magic-tricks       |
| Job           | architect   | mechanic    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | fantasy   |
| Music-Genre   | house      | hip-hop     |
| Sport         | golf | cricket      |
| Transport     | snowmobile       | train           |

