.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, grapefruit
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, pilot
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, nigerian
2 different pets are kept: dog, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, helicopter
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
4. the nigerian is on the left of the coach##1
5. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta         | tea       |
| Food          | lettuce        | grapefruit |
| Job           | pilot | coach    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero        | fantasy  |
| Nationality   | nigerian        | japanese       |
| Pet           | goat            | dog        |
| Transport     | helicopter            | tram       |

