2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the coach is on the left or right of the chef##3
5. the coach is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
