The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, jazz
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, climbing
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, helicopter
1. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is climbing is the person watching epic movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
